<section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-50 to-sky-200 flex flex-col items-center">
  <div class="max-w-4xl flex flex-col py-10 px-5">
    <h3 class="text-5xl font-header uppercase font-semibold">Financing Your Flight Training</h3>
    <h4 class="text-2xl text-gray-800 py-5">Affordable Options to Kickstart Your Aviation Career</h4>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">Dreaming of a career in aviation but concerned about the cost? At Blue Skies Above, we offer a variety of financing options to help make your pilot training more affordable. Our goal is to provide flexible solutions that fit your financial situation, ensuring you can focus on achieving your aviation dreams without the added stress of financial constraints.</p>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 pt-10">
      Whether you're looking for traditional student loans, personal loans, or specialized aviation financing programs, we have partnerships with several financial institutions to offer competitive rates and terms. We also provide guidance and support through the application process, making it easier for you to secure the funds needed for your flight training.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 pt-10">
      Additionally, we offer scholarships and grants for eligible students. Our financial aid advisors are here to help you explore all available options, ensuring you can take the first step towards your career in aviation with confidence. Get in touch with us today to learn more about our financing options and start your journey to becoming a pilot.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
